This point data layer represents addresses for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_Addresses_2014.gdb. This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. The data for this layer was published with multiple feature classes, and the metadata was generated from the "Trempealeau_Addresses_2014" layer. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://tremplocounty.com/landrecords/default.htm. en
